        <methodparam><type>String</type><parameter>identifier</parameter></methodparam>
        <exceptionname>NullPointerException</exceptionname>
        <exceptionname>ClassCastException</exceptionname>
      </methodsynopsis>
      <para>Retrieves a user-scope set variable from the Simulator. </para>
      <para><emphasis>Hint: If you specified a variable in the .msim configuration file you will retrieve it here as a String</emphasis></para>
    </refsect2>
